Tirba Mar Maron li ku ye?
 
Where is the tomb of Mar Maron?

173
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:05,000
Tirba Mar Maron li vir e, li vê derê ye.
 
The tomb of Mar Maron is here, right at this spot.

