Te benî da ye lê?
 
Did you put ties/markers on it?

192
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,000
Na, na, heve.
 
No, no, this is it.

193
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:04,000
Heye, dikirine... kevirê çi ye evir?
 
It is there, they make it... what kind of stone is this
