over there too.

202
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:29,000
Eywa, tewafbûn. Ciyê tewafbûnê ye, belê.
 
Yes, pilgrimage. It is a place of pilgrimage, yes.

203
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:31,000
Belê.
 
Yes.

204
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:34,000
