211
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:51,000
Lê kevirê xwe gi mewcûd in.
 
But its stones are all present.

212
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:57,000
Ka were vir.
 
Come here.

213
00:21:57,000 --> 00:22:00,000
Welle cemekî xweş e.
 
By God, it's a nice place.

214
