Alet tinebûn. Însanê berê...
 
There were no tools. The people of the past...

270
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:16,000
Ew dêwan bûn.
 
They were giants.

271
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:17,000
Evana lo?
 
Were they really?

272
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:24,000
