278
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:40,000
La v'da rakiribandin ne?
 
They lifted it up here, right?

279
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:42,000
Kevir jî giran e, kevriyê xwe giran e.
 
The stone is also heavy, its stone is heavy.

